latestPosts.caption:
A shop/ farmers-market without Salesman/ Shopkeeper found in between Phek-Pfutsero highway.
Integrity and Trust never fails in the rural parts of Nagaland. 

The farmers toiling their day in their respective rice fields without a doubt of keeping their hard earned crops to be sold in this incredible market. They simply place money jars or wooden boxes 📦 to place the money and they put a price tag on top of their vegetables 🍅🍆🥒🥔🥕🌶️🥗🍠🥦🥬🧄🧅🫑🫛

I had the best shopping experiences yesterday 18/09/2024.
